The paper discusses using Markov Chain Monte Carlo (MCMC) methods to solve parameterized control problems, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses control problems in robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY), which are related fields. Additionally, the paper mentions using neural networks (cs.NE) to estimate the optimal policy.
